ower><Date type="date" label="Date" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true" display="localdateshort" UTC="true">20130215T19:00:00</Date><Author type="string" label="Author's Name" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Marc Stevens</Author><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Height=""><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to BYU-Idaho's new blog. As an institution, we're always looking for ways to enhance our communication efforts with news media and the community in general. We hope this blog will help us do that.</p>
<p>Housed within our Newsroom website, the blog will be managed and written by the staff of University Communications.&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.4em;">Watch for posts on university announcements, background information on university news and events, and feature stories on students and employees that will provide additional insight into BYU-Idaho and its institutional mission.</span></p>
<p>There's plenty of great content to come, so check back often. Thanks for reading.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="Component" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="x17620" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Name="News" label="News" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="x28" CompTypes="NewsNavigationComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="List" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><xPower Type="Component" Name="xPower" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes=""/></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navigation" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Expanded="false" Navigation="Ancestors" GenerationOrder="down" StartPage="x5" MaxNodes="" MaxDepth="" Query=""/><xPower Type="Component" Name="SiteControl" label="Site Control" readonly="true" hidden="true" required="false" Component="x10257" CompTypes="SiteControl" Expanded="false"/></NewsDetail>
